// ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
// A.2.7 Expressions
// ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
// ✅: Implemented,  🟥: Not-Implemented, 🟨: Partial


//✅ expression :
//✅     simple-expression
//✅    | if expression then expression { elseif expression then expression } else expression

//🟨  simple-expression :
//✅     logical-expression
//🟥     [ ":" logical-expression [ ":" logical-expression ] ]
pub Expression: ast::Expression = {
    <SimpleExpression> =>  <>,
    "if" <if_cond:SimpleExpression> "then"
    <then_expr:SimpleExpression>
    <else_if_blocks: ElseIfExpressionBlock*>
    <else_expr: ElseExpressionBlock?>
     => {
        let mut if_blocks = Vec::<ast::IfExpressionBlock>::new();
        if_blocks.push(
            ast::IfExpressionBlock {
                cond: if_cond,
                expr: then_expr,
            }
        );
        if_blocks.extend(else_if_blocks);

        ast::Expression::If {
            if_blocks,
            else_expr: Box::new(else_expr),
        }
    },
}

pub ElseIfExpressionBlock: ast::IfExpressionBlock = {
    "elseif" <cond:SimpleExpression> "then" <expr:SimpleExpression>  => {
        ast::IfExpressionBlock {
            cond, expr
        }
    }
}

pub ElseExpressionBlock: ast::Expression = {
    "else" <expr:SimpleExpression> => {
        expr
    }
}

pub ParenthesisExpression = SimpleExpression;

//✅ relational-operator :
//✅    "<" | "<=" | ">" | ">=" | "==" | "<>"
RelationalOperator : ast::BinaryOp = {
    "<" => ast::BinaryOp::LessThan,
    "<=" => ast::BinaryOp::LessThanOrEqual,
    ">" => ast::BinaryOp::GreaterThan,
    ">=" => ast::BinaryOp::GreaterThanOrEqual,
    "==" => ast::BinaryOp::Equal,
    "<>" => ast::BinaryOp::NotEqual,
}

//✅ add-operator :
//✅    "+" | "-" | ".+" | ".-"
AddBinaryOperator : ast::BinaryOp = {
    "+" => ast::BinaryOp::Add,
    "-" => ast::BinaryOp::Sub,
    ".+" => ast::BinaryOp::ElemAdd,
    ".-" => ast::BinaryOp::ElemSub,
}
AddUnaryOperator : ast::UnaryOp = {
    "-" => ast::UnaryOp::Negative,
}

FactorOperator : ast::BinaryOp = {
    "^" => ast::BinaryOp::Exp,
    ".^" => ast::BinaryOp::ElemExp,
}

//✅ mul-operator :
//✅    "*" | "/" | ".*" | "./"
MulOperator : ast::BinaryOp = {
    "*" => ast::BinaryOp::Mul,
    "/" => ast::BinaryOp::Div,
    ".*" => ast::BinaryOp::ElemMul,
    "./" => ast::BinaryOp::ElemDiv,
}

SimpleExpression: ast::Expression = {
//✅ simple-expression :
//✅    logical-expression [ ":" logical-expression [ ":" logical-expression ] ]
    #[precedence(level="11")] #[assoc(side="left")]
    <lhs:SimpleExpression> ":" <rhs:SimpleExpression> => {
        ast::Expression::Binary {
            op: ast::BinaryOp::Range,
            lhs: Box::new(lhs),
            rhs: Box::new(rhs),
        }
    },
//✅ logical-expression :
//✅    logical-term { or logical-term }
    #[precedence(level="10")] #[assoc(side="left")]
    <lhs:SimpleExpression> "or" <rhs:SimpleExpression> => {
        ast::Expression::Binary {
            op: ast::BinaryOp::Or,
            lhs: Box::new(lhs),
            rhs: Box::new(rhs),
        }
    },
//✅ logical-term :
//✅    logical-factor { and logical-factor }
    #[precedence(level="9")] #[assoc(side="left")]
    <lhs:SimpleExpression> "and" <rhs:SimpleExpression> => {
        ast::Expression::Binary {
            op: ast::BinaryOp::Add,
            lhs: Box::new(lhs),
            rhs: Box::new(rhs),
        }
    },
//✅ logical-factor :
//✅    [ not ] relation
    #[precedence(level="8")]
    "not" <rhs:SimpleExpression> => {
        ast::Expression::Unary {
            op: ast::UnaryOp::Not,
            rhs: Box::new(rhs),
        }
    },
//✅ relation :
//✅    arithmetic-expression [ relational-operator arithmetic-expression ]
    #[precedence(level="7")] #[assoc(side="left")]
    <lhs:SimpleExpression> <op:RelationalOperator> <rhs:SimpleExpression> => {
        ast::Expression::Binary {
            op,
            lhs: Box::new(lhs),
            rhs: Box::new(rhs),
        }
    },
//✅ arithmetic-expression :
//✅    [ add-operator ] term { add-operator term }
    #[precedence(level="6")] #[assoc(side="right")]
    <op:AddUnaryOperator> <rhs:SimpleExpression> => {
        ast::Expression::Unary {
            op,
            rhs: Box::new(rhs),
        }
    },
    #[precedence(level="5")] #[assoc(side="left")]
    <lhs:SimpleExpression> <op:AddBinaryOperator> <rhs:SimpleExpression> => {
        ast::Expression::Binary {
            op,
            lhs: Box::new(lhs),
            rhs: Box::new(rhs),
        }
    },
//✅ term :
//✅    factor { mul-operator factor }
    #[precedence(level="4")] #[assoc(side="left")]
    <lhs:SimpleExpression> "*" <rhs:SimpleExpression> => {
        ast::Expression::Binary {
            op: ast::BinaryOp::Mul,
            lhs: Box::new(lhs),
            rhs: Box::new(rhs),
        }
    },
    <lhs:SimpleExpression> ".*" <rhs:SimpleExpression> => {
        ast::Expression::Binary {
            op: ast::BinaryOp::ElemMul,
            lhs: Box::new(lhs),
            rhs: Box::new(rhs),
        }
    },
    <lhs:SimpleExpression> "/" <rhs:SimpleExpression> => {
        ast::Expression::Binary {
            op: ast::BinaryOp::Div,
            lhs: Box::new(lhs),
            rhs: Box::new(rhs),
        }
    },
    <lhs:SimpleExpression> "./" <rhs:SimpleExpression> => {
        ast::Expression::Binary {
            op: ast::BinaryOp::ElemDiv,
            lhs: Box::new(lhs),
            rhs: Box::new(rhs),
        }
    },
//✅ factor :
//✅    primary [ ( "^" | ".^" ) primary ]
    #[precedence(level="3")] #[assoc(side="left")]
    <lhs:SimpleExpression> <op:FactorOperator> <rhs:SimpleExpression> => {
        ast::Expression::Binary {
            op,
            lhs: Box::new(lhs),
            rhs: Box::new(rhs),
        }
    },
//✅ primary :
//✅    UNSIGNED-NUMBER
//🟥    | STRING
//✅    | false
//✅    | true
//✅    | ( component-reference
//✅        | der
//✅        | initial
//✅        | pure ) function-call-args
//✅    | component-reference
//🟥    | "(" output-expression-list ")" [ ( array-subscripts | "." IDENT ) ]
//🟥    | "[" expression-list { ";" expression-list } "]"
//🟥    | "{" array-arguments "}"
//🟥    | end
    #[precedence(level="0")]
    "(" <rhs:ParenthesisExpression> ")" => {
        ast::Expression::Unary {
            op: ast::UnaryOp::Paren,
            rhs: Box::new(rhs)
        }
    },
    "{" <args:SeparatedList<Expression, ",">> "}" => {
        ast::Expression::ArrayArguments {
            args
        }
    },
    <val:"UNSIGNED-INTEGER"> => {
        ast::Expression::UnsignedInteger(val)
    },
    <val:"UNSIGNED-REAL"> => {
        ast::Expression::UnsignedReal(val)
    },
    <val:"boolean"> => {
        ast::Expression::Boolean(val)
    },
    <comp:ComponentReference> => {
        ast::Expression::Ref(comp)
    },
    <comp:ComponentReference> <args:FunctionCallArguments> => {
        ast::Expression::FunctionCall {
            comp,
            args
        }
    },
    "der" <args:FunctionCallArguments> => {
        ast::Expression::Der {
            args
        }
    },
}

//✅ UNSIGNED-NUMBER :
//✅    UNSIGNED-INTEGER | UNSIGNED-REAL
// NOTE: flattened in primary

//✅ type-specifier :
//✅    ["."] name
pub TypeSpecifier: ast::TypeSpecifier = {
    <leading_period: "."?> <name: Name> => {
        ast::TypeSpecifier{
            leading_period: leading_period.is_some(),
            name,
        }
    },
}
//✅ name :
//✅    IDENT { "." IDENT }
pub Name: ast::Name = {
    <first:IDENT> <remaining: ("." <IDENT>)*> => {
        let mut v = vec![first];
        v.extend(remaining);
        ast::Name {
            ident: v
        }
    }
}


//✅ component-reference :
//✅    [ "." ] IDENT [ array-subscripts ] { "." IDENT [ array-subscripts ] }
pub ComponentReference: ast::ComponentReference = {
    <local: "."?> <parts: SeparatedListMinOne<RefPart, ".">> => {
        ast::ComponentReference{
            local: local.is_some(),
            parts,
        }
    },
}
pub RefPart: ast::RefPart = {
    <name:IDENT> <array_subscripts:ArraySubscripts?> => {
        ast::RefPart {
            name,
            array_subscripts: array_subscripts.unwrap_or(Vec::new()),
        }
    }
}

